# VL-JEPA

A simplified, educational implementation of the [VL-JEPA (Vision-Language Joint Embedding Predictive Architecture)](https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.10942) paper, built on Apple MLX.

Adapts the **PaliGemma** VLM into a JEPA architecture (for now).

